<template>
  <v-row>
        <v-btn
        depressed
        color="primary"
        @click="ClickCreateNew()"
        >
        Primary
        </v-btn>
  </v-row>
</template>

<script>
import Factory from '@/server/factory/factory';
import common from '@/server/common/common';
const New = Factory.get('new');
export default {
    data() {
        return {
             //userlogin
            ma_ND: null,
            ten_NV: null,
            token: null,
            quyen_ID:null,
        }
    },
    methods: {
        ClickCreateNew() {
            console.log("start "+this.token);
            var month='08/2020';
             New.Get_List_New(month,self.token).then(response =>{
                if(response.data.success && response.data.data.length){
                    self.desserts = response.data.data;
                    self.loading=false
                    self.text="Lấy dữ liệu hoàn tất";
                    self.snackbar=true;
                }

            });
        }
    },
    created () {
        var self=this;

        //Get Info User Login
        var UserLogin = common.GetInfoUserLogin('token_session');
        if(!UserLogin)
        self.$router.push('/login');
        else
        {
        self.ten_NV=UserLogin.ten_NV;
        self.ma_ND=UserLogin.ma_ND;
        self.token=UserLogin.token;
        self.quyen_ID=UserLogin.quyen_ID;
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
